# 
Leno Design System

## Color Palette

### Light Mode
```dart
// Main Background
shellWhite: Color(0xFFFCFBFB)      // Soft, neutral white

// Main Text
darkGraphite: Color(0xFF2F2F2F)    // Primary text color

// UI Panels (Cards, Navigation)
panelWhite: Color(0xFFFFFFFF)      // Pure white

// Accent Color (Buttons, Links, Alerts)
softCoral: Color(0xFFFF7A8A)       // Warm, friendly, represents "love"

// Secondary Information
mediumGray: Color(0xFF909090)      // Secondary text
```

### Dark Mode
```dart
// Main Background
deepPlum: Color(0xFF1F1B1E)        // Deep black with subtle purple-red tone

// Main Text
softWhite: Color(0xFFEDEAEB)       // Soft white text

// UI Panels (Cards, Navigation)
darkGray: Color(0xFF2A2629)        // Same color family as background

// Accent Color (same as light mode)
softCoral: Color(0xFFFF7A8A)       // Stands out without being too sweet

// Secondary Information (same as light mode)
mediumGray: Color(0xFF909090)
```

## Typography
- **Font Family**: System default (Inter-like on iOS, Roboto on Android)
- **Hierarchy**:
  - H1: 28-32px, Bold (Page titles)
  - H2: 22-24px, Bold (Section headers)
  - H3: 18-20px, SemiBold (Card titles)
  - Body: 14-16px, Regular (Main content)
  - Caption: 12-13px, Regular (Secondary info)

## UI Components Style

### Cards
- Border Radius: 16-20px (rounded-2xl)
- Shadow: Subtle, soft shadows
- Padding: 16-20px
- Background: panelWhite (light) / darkGray (dark)

### Buttons
- Primary: softCoral background, white text
- Border Radius: Full (rounded-full for pills)
- Active State: scale(0.95) transition
- Shadow: Medium shadow for elevation

### Icons
- Size: 20-24px for UI elements
- Color: mediumGray for inactive, softCoral for active
- Style: Lucide icons (use similar Material/Cupertino icons)

### Navigation
- Bottom Tab Bar: 90px height
- Backdrop Blur: 80% opacity with blur effect
- Active Tab: softCoral color with bold text
- Inactive Tab: mediumGray with regular text

## Animation Guidelines
- Transitions: 200-300ms duration
- Easing: Ease-in-out for smooth feel
- Micro-interactions: Button press, tab switch
- Avoid: Excessive animations that distract

## Layout Principles
- Spacing: 8px base unit (multiples of 8)
- Margins: 16-20px horizontal padding
- Grid: 2-column for post cards, 3-column for image galleries
- Safe Area: Respect iOS notch and Android system bars
